2. China COVID-19 lockdowns
3. Fed expected rate hike on Wed.

Brent (INT) @ $99.91

In this war, NATO is essentially providing weapons to Ukraine, money to Russia and hollow threats to the remaining countries.  ft.com/content/865ee6…
